 CD-MAN  Pre-release June 89                               Pre-release Specials
컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴

In this pre-release there is an endless life function for testing purposes.

The endless life will only work in one player mode.

At any point during gameplay you can press F1 ( that is the first function key )
to gain endless life, you will still 'die' as usual but the number of lifes
will not be decremented.

If you press F1 a second time you will be mortal again and so on...

There is no way ( exept dying ) to see what mode you are in, so you'll have
to keep track of that yourself.

At the start of a new game endless life is always off.








